      "Distributional Overlap Metrics:\n",
      "  Centroid cosine similarity:        0.9399\n",
      "    (1.0 = identical distributions, <0.9 = divergent)\n",
      "  Cross-source mean cosine sim:      0.3511 ± 0.1467\n",
      "  Within-original mean cosine sim:   0.4169 ± 0.1593\n",
      "  Within-synthetic mean cosine sim:  0.3386 ± 0.1503\n",
